author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Gyedu-Blay Ambolley performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded July 15, 2025.

Songs: 
Simigwa-Do 02:27
Teacher 07:09
Afrika Yie 14:59
U Like Or U No Like 21:47

Gyedu-Blay Ambolley - Vocals, Tenor Sax
